_sText: This is a map I have been working on and off for a long time.  Takes about 10 - 14 mins to beat.  Mostly climb, without the kz triggers.  If you want an estimate of how long this took to make, probably 7 months.  I wasn't working on this every day, but I went back and changed a lot of stuff.  This map should be possible for legit.  Not the most fun on legit, but I didn't want to exclude anyone.  Also I added skips, but they add 20 seconds to your time.  Either do the Long Jumps or do the skip if you can't do the Long Jumps. Enjoy.
